    2. -> Context or ContextAPI
          it is used to manage the global state. For this, we don't need any 3rd party library 
    
          lifting up state have problem that is props drelling
    
        
          to avoid this props drelling  problem context are used 
    
       -> 3 steps involed in context API
        1. create Context
            createContext — creates the global store
        2. Provider
            Provider — wraps components and shares value
        3. Consumer
            useContext — any child reads from the store directly
            -> first we create a context and provide that context to the prarent component with values
               and we consume this context in any of the child and subchild of the parent component any where.
            ->  when there is any change in the context it automatically updated where it is consume..   
        
     


